                     <interp inst="t18161204-102-verdict555" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               Recommended to Mercy by the Prosecutor
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18161204-102-punish556" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18161204-102-punish556" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
